  = must: treat compress_first as the dominant near-term disposition
  = must: treat index_ready as permission for read-only lookup and kernel-bundle preparation, not model training
  = must: keep Task_161 ready but precede it with compact manager kernel bundle if possible
  = must: keep LM Studio manager proposal-only until Codex accepts a handoff candidate
